    <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 rounded-lg p-4 border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
      <p class="text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-300 mb-3">
        Be careful if someone you don't know asks you to send money, especially if:
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
          </svg>
          <span>They claim to be from a government office</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
          </svg>
          <span>They say you've won a prize or lottery</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
          </svg>
          <span>They create a sense of urgency or emergency</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
          </svg>
          <span>They ask for your PIN or password</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- What to do if you sent money by mistake -->
  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white flex items-center">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-red-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      What to Do If You Send Money by Mistake
    </h3>
    
    <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg p-4 border-l-4 border-red-500">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        <span class="text-lg font-medium text-red-800 dark:text-red-300">Act quickly!</span>
      </div>
      
      <ol class="list-decimal ml-6 space-y-2 text-red-800 dark:text-red-300">
        <li>Call the recipient immediately and ask them to return the money</li>
        <li>Contact our support team right away at <strong>+233 XX XXX XXXX</strong></li>
        <li>Provide the transaction details (ID, amount, recipient, date/time)</li>
        <li>Do not send additional money if the recipient asks for fees to return your money</li>
      </ol>
      
      <div class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-red-200 dark:border-red-800">
        <a href="tel:+233XXXXXXXXX" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
          </svg>
          Call Support Now
